data.description: The home sits on 7.4+/- acres of privacy with a partially wooded lot and a gated drive convenient to both Cleveland & Chattanooga, TN as well as Dalton, GA.  The home was fully renovated in 2017-2018 and it is one to see!  The original home was taken down to the studs and remade--new framing, new windows, new insulation, new electrical, new plumbing, new roof, TWO new TRANE HVAC units etc. with KitchenAid appliances!  This one is hard to beat. You'll love the open concept of the main level with the family room, dining room and kitchen--great neutral colors and you'll love the ceiling.  Beautiful cabinetry, countertops, and so many custom touches.Both barns and the huge workshop/garage have power and water--great place to call  home!
